1
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:01,280
Sanniang.

2
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:03,140
Why are you sleeping here?

3
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,360
Go back to bed.

4
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,120
Sanniang.

5
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:17,640
Sanniang,

6
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,400
wake up!

7
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:21,039
Sanniang.

8
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,320
Yan Mingli.

9
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,600
Yan Mingli.

10
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:41,650
Where are you going?

11
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:44,080
I'm going to kill her.

12
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,880
You can't go now.

13
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:46,920
Lady Zhou and Xie Yuheng

14
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:48,180
are with her right now.

15
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,680
Going there is throwing your life away.

16
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,240
Move.

17
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,280
Move!

18
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,120
I told you to get out of the way!

19
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,759
Calm down.

20
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,200
If you barge in like this,

21
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,140
all our previous plans

22
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,480
will be ruined.

23
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,370
Trust me.

24
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,720
I will make them

25
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,320
pay with their blood.

26
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,290
Qingshu.

27
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:35,040
Prepare a coffin.

28
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:42,400
Qingshu.

29
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,560
Qingshu,

30
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,360
I have come to marry you.

31
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,220
Drinking alone late at night,

32
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,200
Lord Xiao is in a good mood.

33
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,490
You saw through my identity after all.

34
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,280
When I saved you that day,

35
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,320
On your waist tag,

36
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,769
the words Zhenbei Marquis Mansion

37
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,880
are still fresh in my memory.

38
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:23,880
Since Lord Xiao was willing to disguise as a merchant,

39
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,460
I naturally played along.

40
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,330
But I don't understand.

41
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:31,520
Why would the dignified heir of Zhenbei Marquis

42
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,740
want to cooperate with me,

43
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,440
a duke's daughter with an empty title?

44
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,520
The whole court knows

45
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,560
that the Duke colluded with the enemy and committed treason,

46
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,960
but that is not the truth.

47
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,020
You believe me.

48
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,250
You believe my father is innocent.

49
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,920
Both our fathers

50
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,800
were deeply loyal

51
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,159
and devoted.

52
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,400
But they were framed by Prince Ling,

53
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,560
bore a bad name,

54
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,850
and suffered unredressed injustice.

55
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,120
But my father

56
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:17,520
is missing now,

57
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:20,000
and his fate is unknown.

58
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,160
Rest assured.

59
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,130
Since I promised you

60
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,960
to help you find the Duke,

61
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,290
I will not break my promise.

62
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,570
Qingshu,

63
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,960
as long as you believe me.

64
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,560
Tomorrow

65
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,640
will be Xie Yuheng's death.

66
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,700
Your Highness,

67
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,480
the eagle flag of the Right Wise King of Beidi

68
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,240
has appeared by the Black Water River.

69
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,240
Tomorrow's situation.

70
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,760
Should we proceed with the original plan?

71
00:06:30,760 --> 00:06:32,480
The arrow is on the bow string, it must be fired.

72
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:34,140
Everything remains the same.

73
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,120
I still have a doubt.

74
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,490
Why did you, My Lord,

75
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,320
approach Ms. Yan

76
00:06:41,400 --> 00:06:42,880
as Ren Jiuxiao in the first place?

77
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,280
Now you reveal your identity at this moment,

78
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,610
aren't you afraid of unexpected changes?

79
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:50,720
Qingshu has always been hostile to the Xiao family.

80
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,450
At that time,

81
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,800
I didn't know how much she knew about the old grudge.

82
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,930
If I approached her rashly as the heir,

83
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,460
how could she trust me?

84
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:02,700
She wouldn't have followed me to the capital to plot great things.

85
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,720
Now the game has started,

86
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,940
with danger at every step.

87
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,540
We have a common enemy,

88
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,960
so we should be honest with each other.

89
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:13,690
The identity of the heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei

90
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,100
can give her the blade of revenge.

91
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,800
You are very thoughtful, My Lord.

92
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,280
It is beyond my capability.

93
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,080
I understand.

94
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,560
My son and Qingshu

95
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:29,560
have been engaged since childhood.

96
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:32,120
When she comes of age, if they are in love,

97
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:34,040
this half-jade will serve as a token.

98
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:37,040
Although incomplete, it can reflect the sun and moon.

99
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,560
Sir, your dishes are all here. Enjoy your meal.

100
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,560
Sir, please come inside and take a seat.

101
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,620
Xiaowu.

102
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,040
Why the panic?

103
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:05,760
Boss, look.

104
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,040
A person in a bamboo hat and white clothes

105
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,240
stuffed it into my hand and ran.

106
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,600
That person moved so fast,

107
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:13,000
disappeared without a trace in an instant.

108
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,530
Alright, I know.

109
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:17,700
Go back to work.

110
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,800
Yes, boss.

111
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,080
That day at Zhuque Tower.

112
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,120
I failed to recognize Your Highness.

113
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,320
I hope you can forgive me, Xiao.

114
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,960
Your Highness condescends to visit late at night.

115
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:42,320
Did you come for the Marquis of Zhenbei?

116
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:43,760
If you have any orders,

117
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:46,160
I will do my best.

118
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,840
Orders?

119
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,200
I came here tonight

120
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,960
to settle an old score.

121
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,560
I and Your Highness

122
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:05,020
have never crossed paths.

123
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,720
How can there be an old score to settle?

124
00:09:11,680 --> 00:09:12,720
Xie Yuheng.

125
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:17,480
Your hands, used to holding the pure brush of the Hanlin Academy

126
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,680
and correcting beautiful articles,

127
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,480
have they ever been stained with

128
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,360
a mother's blood?

129
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:36,720
The Marquis's loyalty is witnessed by heaven and earth.

130
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,450
He would never commit treason.

131
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:39,920
Lord Xie,

132
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,240
what will it take

133
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:45,760
for you to withdraw the joint impeachment

134
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,960
and speak up for the Marquis?

135
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,000
You want me to save Xiao Muyu?

136
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:52,840
Sure.

137
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,640
A life for a life.

138
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,400
You die,

139
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:00,560
he lives.

140
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,200
Xie Wanshu,

141
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,650
remember what you said.

142
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:12,280
A life for a life.

143
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:15,320
I die, the Marquis lives.

144
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:18,300
If you dare to break your oath,

145
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:23,200
my soul will fall into hell and become an Asura,

146
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:25,880
haunting you for your life forever.

147
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,760
You... you're crazy.

148
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,570
You must be joking, Your Highness.

149
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:52,800
The Xie family has been upright and pure for generations,

150
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:54,080
wielding the Hanlin brush

151
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,810
and reading the books of sages.

152
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,600
My hands

153
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,960
are completely clean.

154
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,420
How could they be stained with blood?

155
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,100
Your Highness,

156
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:15,840
try this tea.

157
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,530
Junshan Silver Needle,

158
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,120
the most elegant tea.

159
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:23,140
It is perfect for entertaining distinguished guests.

160
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,400
I will skip the tea.

161
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:27,040
I have a stomachache.

162
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:29,060
May I use your latrine?

163
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,760
Then I will have a servant

164
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,160
show you the way, Your Highness.

165
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:33,680
No need.

166
00:11:34,920 --> 00:11:37,050
At Old Master Xie's birthday banquet,

167
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:38,850
I was here to congratulate him.

168
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,660
Where your latrine is,

169
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,120
I still have

170
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,440
that much memory.

171
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,040
Then, Your Highness,

172
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:48,100
please make yourself at home.

173
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,280
Your Highness!

174
00:13:02,160 --> 00:13:03,160
Your Highness!

175
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,000
Xie Yuheng,

176
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,880
I just borrowed

177
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,280
your toilet for a moment.

178
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,800
There's no need to make such a fuss about it, right?

179
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,460
The things in that storehouse

180
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:15,600
are nothing but dusty old items.

181
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:17,280
If Your Highness likes them,

182
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:18,800
just ask.

183
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:21,040
How could I not be willing to part with them?

184
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:24,440
Why resort to stealing?

185
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:30,940
It truly demeans your status as the Heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei.

186
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,120
Loose arrows!

187
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,200
Xiao Jingyan!

188
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:12,320
Cuimei.

189
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,530
Huachao.

190
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:16,880
Weikun, Huachao.

191
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,160
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

192
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:23,280
Shuang, Bin.

193
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:23,640
Shuang.

194
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:24,080
Shuang, Bin.

195
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,720
Ning Zheng.

196
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,480
Ning Zheng.

197
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:29,280
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

198
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,010
Weichao.

199
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:33,720
Wei, Chao.

200
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,440
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

201
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:51,920
Xi.

202
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:53,960
Xi.

203
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,560
Taoqiang.

204
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:55,160
Taoqiang.

205
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:00,320
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

206
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,320
Yiyi.

207
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,520
Si, Si.
